{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/github-page/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bbahna"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"743e1687-006e-5ea8-bd4a-6becf46e4a51","excerpt":"기술 블로그로 Gatsby를 선택한 후, 서버 배포에 대해 고민하다 github-page를 이용하여 배포하기로 하였습니다.\ngithub와 연동이 되며 사용법이 어렵지 않다는 장점으로 선택하게 되었습니다. 1. github-page repository 생성 repository name: \n 2. gatsby template 선택 gatsby template…","html":"<p> 기술 블로그로 <strong>Gatsby</strong>를 선택한 후, 서버 배포에 대해 고민하다 <strong>github-page를 이용하여 배포</strong>하기로 하였습니다.<br />\n<strong>github와 연동</strong>이 되며 <strong>사용법이 어렵지 않다</strong>는 장점으로 선택하게 되었습니다.</p>\n<h2>1. github-page repository 생성</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>repository name: <code class=\"language-text\">계정.github.io</code>\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/78d47/github-page(1).png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 56.470588235294116%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='github page 1 ' title='github page 1 ' src='/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/ca1dc/github-page(1).png' srcset='/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/e7570/github-page(1).png 170w,\n/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/f46e7/github-page(1).png 340w,\n/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/ca1dc/github-page(1).png 680w,\n/static/d3cb170d8ea1e96a28095bf2ccbc6590/78d47/github-page(1).png 800w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2. gatsby template 선택</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>gatsby template는 <a href=\"https://github.com/devHudi/gatsby-starter-hoodie\">gatsby-starter-hoodie</a> 결정</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>나의 template 선택조건</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>다크모드, 검색, 태그, 댓글기능</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>추가로 <a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/gatsby-starter-bee\">gatsby-starter-bee</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/sungik-choi/gatsby-starter-apple\">gatsby-starter-apple</a>도 마지막까지 고민한 템플릿입니다.<br/>\n공식 홈페이지에서도 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters/\">template</a>를 제공하고 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>3. gatsby template clone</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>gatsby cli 설치<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install -g gatsby-cli</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn global add gatsby-cli</code></li>\n<li>project 생성<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ gatsby new {project-name} {template-route}</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ gatsby new bbahna.github.io https://github.com/devHudi/gatsby-starter-hoodie</code></li>\n<li>개발 설정<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ cd bbahna.github.io</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ gatsby develop</code> 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn develop</code></li>\n<li>git 연결<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ rm -rf .git</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ git init</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ git remote add origin https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io.git</code></li>\n<li>원격 저장소에 소스 올리기<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ git add .</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ git commit -m “init”</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ git push origin master</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4. customizing</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/blob/master/blog-config.js\">blog-config.js 수정</a></li>\n<li>favicon, profile, link image 변경</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5. github page <strong>호스팅</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>gh-pages 설치<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ npm i gh-pages</code><br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn add gh-pages --dev</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>6. <strong>github actions</strong> 배포 자동화(CI/CD)</h2>\n<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/settings/tokens\">token 발급</a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/commit/01b0684c08700088b8c2b152bb9662c5b913a3ef\">자동 build token 설정</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>.<a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/blob/master/.github/workflows/ci.yml\">github/workflows/ci.yml</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">with<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\n\taccess-token<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.BBAHNA_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\tdeploy-branch<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> gh-pages</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/commit/759b0a9bb288a4e5f8847f4f46fddb49320752f3\">Create main.yml</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/blob/master/.github/workflows/main.yml\">.github/workflows/main.yml</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">access-token<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.BBAHNA_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>새글 생성</p>\n<ul>\n<li>contents/posts/post-name/index.md<br/>\n<em><strong>url: bbahna.gitbhub.io/post-name</strong></em></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bbahna/bbahna.github.io/actions\">Action</a> 확인</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Gatsby 배포특징</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>가공할 정보를 GraphQL에서 가져와서 <strong>Build 과정에서 마크업 생성</strong></li>\n<li>배포할 때 각 페이지 정보들이 모두 만들어지므로 따로 서버가 필요하지 않다.<br/>\n↔ SPA(Single Page Application): JavaScript가 실행되면 빈 HTML 페이지 안에 마크업을 추가</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>**검색엔진 최적화</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>추후 업데이트 예정 :)</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 개발기록 _github page 배포설정","date":"May 01, 2022","update":"May 01, 2022","tags":["github","build","cicd","TIL"],"series":"Gatsby"},"fields":{"slug":"/github-page/","readingTime":{"minutes":2.22}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"f1474a49-d897-5585-88b7-6d56608225a4","fields":{"slug":"/js-framework/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"기술 블로그에 Gatsby를 사용한 이유"}}},{"node":{"id":"743e1687-006e-5ea8-bd4a-6becf46e4a51","fields":{"slug":"/github-page/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby 개발기록 _github page 배포설정"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/js-framework/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"기술 블로그에 Gatsby를 사용한 이유"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/application-rendering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSR, SSR / SPA, MPA에 대한 이해"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"743e1687-006e-5ea8-bd4a-6becf46e4a51","series":"Gatsby","previousPostId":"f1474a49-d897-5585-88b7-6d56608225a4","nextPostId":"6aaa3ee5-3ed4-58b6-808b-0ffe82d761d6"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}